libbpf: Reduce bpf_core_apply_relo_insn() stack usage.

Reduce bpf_core_apply_relo_insn() stack usage and bump
BPF_CORE_SPEC_MAX_LEN limit back to 64.

Fixes: 29db4bea1d10 ("bpf: Prepare relo_core.c for kernel duty.")
